{
  "page": "Howling Hill",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><dl><dd><i>For the hills in Essos, see <a href=\"/index.php/Howling_Hills\" title=\"Howling Hills\">Howling Hills</a>.</i></dd></dl>\n<p>The <b>Howling Hill</b> is a hill in the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">stormlands</a> whose exact location has been lost to history.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Howling_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood_Alliance\" title=\"Weirwood Alliance\">Weirwood Alliance</a> between <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a> defeated <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a> beneath the Howling Hill.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Howling_Hill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\